    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior shows significant signs of neglect, including noticeable rust patches on the wheel arches, several large dents, and heavily faded paint. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and currently struggles to stay running, while the interior features torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. While it has served its purpose over the years, it will require a substantial investment in both time and money to return it to a roadworthy state.",
